title: Rubbish Thai Waitress Services On All Fours
description: Throwing prawns and vegetables into a vat of boiling stock, and then trying to eat them with chopsticks, bloody hell, what a meal. But the waitress was delightful, always smiling, and asking if I wanted anything else. So I kept ordering more stuff, so I could watch her slim figure as she negotiated the aisle. I paid the bill. Again she asked if there was anything else I wanted. "Yes girl, I want you naked on all fours on the floor of my apartment." She flinched barely perceptibly, but kept smiling, and said, "I cannot, I have boyfriend, I am not rubbish girl." Amazing what a good tip can do, watch slim sexy Emkay on video, waiting on my cock and smiling.
